{"id": "1251150457263489164", "channel_id": "1251125266101702727", "type": 0, "author_id": "1172138340275994645", "author_name": "cpeax_34497", "author_bot": false, "content": "我当初就是因为幻梦流程太长所以才打相位的，没想到又要回去打幻梦", "timestamp": "2024-06-14T12:25:14.263000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1251125266101702727", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "每次打相位都是在坐牢", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168158678204497"]}
{"id": "1251150948613623840", "channel_id": "1251125266101702727", "type": 0, "author_id": "611608223983599616", "author_name": "jackpot_7", "author_bot": false, "content": "嗯 可以理解 首勝是這樣的 低難度應該是能打挺快的", "timestamp": "2024-06-14T12:27:11.410000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1251125266101702727", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "每次打相位都是在坐牢", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168158678204497"]}
{"id": "1251151678326181988", "channel_id": "1251125266101702727", "type": 0, "author_id": "1172138340275994645", "author_name": "cpeax_34497", "author_bot": false, "content": "事后反馈之幻梦：幻梦好像更新了短路线（至少这次是这样），对我这样的要求速通的选手非常友好，太好了", "timestamp": "2024-06-14T12:30:05.387000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "👍", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1251125266101702727", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "每次打相位都是在坐牢", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168158678204497"]}
{"id": "1251162404134322176", "channel_id": "1251125266101702727", "type": 0, "author_id": "676337286769672192", "author_name": "hailananxie7110", "author_bot": false, "content": "幻夢打低等級，可以直接撞王", "timestamp": "2024-06-14T13:12:42.619000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1251125266101702727", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "每次打相位都是在坐牢", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168158678204497"]}
{"id": "1251183125426344049", "channel_id": "1251125266101702727", "type": 0, "author_id": "1045141709580927067", "author_name": "luoqixikiss", "author_bot": false, "content": "这是啥博弈啊，运气游戏呐，只要带了权杖，毒队可以投了，带了麻痹，萝坦可以投了。谁先抽上来组建，谁就赢了。墨菲3费算力加2起手就已经赢了一半了，完全感觉不到博弈，慢慢的运气感!", "timestamp": "2024-06-14T14:35:02.960000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1251125266101702727", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "每次打相位都是在坐牢", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168158678204497"]}
{"id": "1251184681593081856", "channel_id": "1251125266101702727", "type": 19, "author_id": "655338276554801152", "author_name": "arr5721", "author_bot": false, "content": "墨菲確實沒啥好說的\n但毒隊你能搭阿格，帶好阿格鑰令\n蘿坦基本上都會帶雙驅，麻痺比較沒問題，怕的是點殺（因為基本上是單核", "timestamp": "2024-06-14T14:41:13.979000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["1045141709580927067"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1251183125426344049", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1251125266101702727", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "每次打相位都是在坐牢", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168158678204497"]}
{"id": "1251200063158353971", "channel_id": "1251125266101702727", "type": 0, "author_id": "1045141709580927067", "author_name": "luoqixikiss", "author_bot": false, "content": "我玩的就是鲨鱼加玫瑰命伦，玩儿的就是打你的单核", "timestamp": "2024-06-14T15:42:21.230000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1251125266101702727", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "每次打相位都是在坐牢", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168158678204497"]}
{"id": "1251200478495375451", "channel_id": "1251125266101702727", "type": 0, "author_id": "1045141709580927067", "author_name": "luoqixikiss", "author_bot": false, "content": "除非遇到运气狗，不公平都能选到缠绕，而且最幽默的是权杖被缠绕了还解不了缠绕。权杖解不了缠绕才是最搞笑的好吧，4费的命伦啊。。。。", "timestamp": "2024-06-14T15:44:00.254000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1251125266101702727", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "每次打相位都是在坐牢", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168158678204497"]}
{"id": "1251200807689388133", "channel_id": "1251125266101702727", "type": 0, "author_id": "1045141709580927067", "author_name": "luoqixikiss", "author_bot": false, "content": "反正博弈完全没有博弈感，基本都是运气好直接拿下，运气不好核心组件给你留箱底。人机都能爆杀你", "timestamp": "2024-06-14T15:45:18.740000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1251125266101702727", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "每次打相位都是在坐牢", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168158678204497"]}
{"id": "1251207347414634578", "channel_id": "1251125266101702727", "type": 19, "author_id": "655338276554801152", "author_name": "arr5721", "author_bot": false, "content": "權杖這部分我倒是覺得比較有博弈性質了\n首先，對手沒上異常手段這張就是廢卡；其次，你能改變站位使預想的核心命輪與蛇杖不被同時纏繞(當然遇到阿格的話也沒辦法，但阿格也就只有那效果而已)；再來，由於沒有綁死喚醒體，能存著看時機使用(也別說這太沒用，看看同樣是全體驅散還不會被纏繞的汀有多少人用)\n~~當然如果對手玩毒手又很順沒機會用就死也是可能的，不過卡牌嘛，能完全counter的話那開場看陣容就直接投打牌幹嘛~~", "timestamp": "2024-06-14T16:11:17.932000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2024-06-14T16:19:40.635000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": ["1045141709580927067"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1251200478495375451", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1251125266101702727", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "每次打相位都是在坐牢", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168158678204497"]}
{"id": "1251207858486247488", "channel_id": "1251125266101702727", "type": 0, "author_id": "655338276554801152", "author_name": "arr5721", "author_bot": false, "content": "目前來說太吃核心組件確實是個問題，特別是這版開場全體20狂氣，很快就能進入爆發，導致第一輪牌庫很可能都沒抽齊<:flop:1236937860922343466> ，正版麻毒隊我更是一場都沒打贏過，但整體而言我覺得還算不錯啦", "timestamp": "2024-06-14T16:13:19.781000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1251125266101702727", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "每次打相位都是在坐牢", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168158678204497"]}
